imdb.plot outline: The 1959 Vehico CAR was billed as the most advanced vehicle of its time, promising to take you where no one has ever gone before. However, on the eve of the 1959 Detroit Auto Show, something went wrong terribly wrong, and time has stood still ever since. People are rarely seen nowadays, and the next species to dominate the country have taken over - deer. All the while, CAR has been rusting away, until one day when a mysterious monkey shows up at CAR's garage with promises of fulfilling their shared destiny of going to the moon.
imdb.title: Monkey & Car
plot: Set in 1959 Detroit Michigan, a Monkey and Car stumble upon each other only to discover a shared fate, and work as a team to fulfill their destiny of going to the moon.::David Rocco Facchini
